NOTICE: IF YOU ARE NEW TO UE4 AND PLAN TO ADD YOUR OWN WEAPONS, KNOWLEDGE OF GAME ANIMATIONS AND ANIMATION BLUEPRINTS IS HIGHLY RECOMMENDED. THIS IS NOT STREAMLINED TO WORK WITH ANY WEAPON ASSET OTHER THAN FPSK READY WEAPONS WHICH PREPARES SIGHT/MUZZLE/GRIP ATTACHMENTS, GRIP POSES, SHOOT SLOT ANIMATIONS, WEAPON SWAY ETC.
